DISCRETIONARY APPEALS ALLOWED

95-100. Trader v. People Working Coop., Inc. Hamilton County, No. C-930716.

Discretionary appeal allowed; swa sponte, cause held for the decision in 94-405, Haynes v. Zoological Soc. of Cincinnati, Hamilton County, Nos. C-910598 and C-910635; briefing schedule stayed.

Douglas and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., dissent.
